@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vipxjp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.43 - v1 + 0.15)))
    v1 = ((0.27 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.20)) * ((v2 + 0.35 * v0 + 0.80) + wp.exp(v1 + 0.10)))
    tmp = (0.25 - wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.60)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
